collection_holder_name: Noel Memorial Library, Northwest Louisiana Archives at LSUS
pageContext.collection_description: Includes scrapbooks, 1948-1965, with photographs, newspaper clippings, correspondence and ephemera related to The Register, the radio and television broadcasts hosted by the paper's publisher, Orene Muse (Mrs. Elton Huckabay) in the 1940s-1950s.
